loads/2025/03/Haim.-Credit_-Lea-Garn-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Haim.-Credit_-Lea-Garn-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Haim.-Credit_-Lea-Garn-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Haim">海姆（Haim）</a>用微风的新单曲“关系”标记了他们的卷土重来。在下面查看。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/haim-live-in-london-setlist-photos-all-points-east-3489973">Haim Live in London：姐妹们大幅重返精神家园</a></strong></li></ul><p>由Rostam Batmanglij（ <a href="/artists/Vampire-Weekend">Vampire Weekend</a> ， <a href="/artsits/Clairo">Clairo</a> ）和Danielle Haim制作的Breezy Pop Track看到了由Danielle，Este和Alana组成的Sister Trio，探索了“所有这些关于关系的谈论？”的问题。</p><p>这是幻想和可跳舞的合唱团看到丹妮尔·辛格（Danielle Sing）： <em>“我听到脑海中的声音，它一直在问我为什么在这种恋爱关系中 /宝贝，当一个无辜的错误变成17天 /他妈的关系时，我该如何解释。</em>透明</p><p>曲目还看到乐队采取了更脆弱的方法，问： <em>“他们最终不是一样 /当没有人要责备 /我认为我恋爱了，但我无法忍受他妈的关系”</em> 。</p><p>由卡米尔·萨默斯·瓦利（Camille Summers-Valli）执导的歌曲随附的音乐视频明星演员德鲁·斯塔基（Drew Starkey）是丹妮尔（Danielle）对衰落的关系的热爱兴趣，而她的姐妹们则帮助她打包了她的东西。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Haim-关系（官方视频）" width="696" height="522" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dOI_QTmK8Ks?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>该曲目今天早些时候以英国广播电台1的最热门唱片为首演，并成为Haim即将到来的第四张LP的第一个品尝者。新闻稿称“关系”“与即将发行的专辑的摇滚声音形成了鲜明对比。”</p><p>为了取笑他们的新时代，该小组以前在Tiktok剪辑中分享了“关系”的片段，使他们在浴室里跳舞和唱歌。他们还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haim-announce-new-comeback-single-relationships-3843900">自己的Instagram上</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haim-announce-new-comeback-single-relationships-3843900">分享了单身的合作</a>艺术<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haim-announce-new-comeback-single-relationships-3843900">。</a></p><p>然后，姐妹们上个月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/haim-appear-to-be-teasing-their-long-awaited-comeback-new-single-3838268">在丹妮尔（Danielle）举行的36岁生日聚会上</a>分享了一个Instagram帖子，上面写着：“（ha）我是单身.. haim单身吗？” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DG01BJwtjGT/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.114 551.658,50 C551.658,55.887 546.887,60.657 541,60.657 M541,33.886 C532.1,33.886 524.886,41.1 524.886,50 C524.886,58.899 532.1,66.113 541,66.113 C549.9,66.113 557.115,58.899 557.115,50 C557.115,41.1 549.9,33.886 541,33.886 M565.378,62.101 C5